A '''Lannister bannerman''' is an unnamed recurring background character in the [[Season 2|second]] and [[Season 3|third seasons]]. He is played by an unidentified extra and debuts in &quot;[[The Ghost of Harrenhal]].&quot; He is fighting for Lord [[Tywin Lannister]] in the [[War of the Five Kings]].

sections.Biography:
===[[Season 2]]===
He attends the war council of [[Tywin Lannister]] at [[Harrenhal]]. Also present are Ser [[Amory Lorch]], [[Reginald Lannister]] and two other bannermen.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[The Ghost of Harrenhal]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt; He is also present when Tywin reprimands Ser Amory for his illiteracy.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[The Old Gods and the New]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt; He is again present when Ser [[Kevan Lannister]] and Tywin discuss leaving Harrenhal.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[The Prince of Winterfell]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

===[[Season 3]]===
He attends the wedding of [[Tyrion Lannister]] and [[Sansa Stark]].&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Second Sons (episode)|Second Sons]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
